|-
| [[File:Razor_Fang.png|20px]] [[Razor Fang]] || 50 [[File:Blue_Shard_Updated.png|20px]] [[Blue Shard|Blue Shards]] <br> 75 [[File:Lime_Shard_Updated.png|20px]] Lime Shards || 625 {{Questpoints}}
|}

For details as to where one can purchase these items, please check the [[Shard Trader]] page for more information.

==Acquisition==
Lime Shards can be found in the [[Underground]], traded for with the [[Berry Master|Hoenn Berry Master]], and as Loot in [[Dungeons]].

